reviews.review_text: It was Fine I was lucky enough to be there. Brent was emerging (after only 8 years) I'M as a loss of words but this recording took me back. Little bunny foo foo. thanks

oh well Problems whole show and Weir is out of tune and having a rough time w/equipment. Some decent effort (and a few very nice moments) here and there but sort of a lowest test score of an otherwise great spring/summer.
